cu.explanation_en: Setting the physical layer log level to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause logging configuration failure and prevent proper physical layer log initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting the physical layer log level to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause logging configuration failure and prevent proper physical layer log initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將物理層日誌等級設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致日誌配置失敗，並阻止正確的物理層日誌初始化。
